  {
    "id": "0708fd03-7a36-4a8c-ac6a-0af43b8d741b",
    "slug": "german-phone-video-call-phrases-italian",
    "title": "Frasi Tedesche per Telefonare e Videochiamare il Tuo Partner",
    "links_added": 1,
    "content_html": "<p>Immagina di svegliarti accanto al tuo partner tedesco e poterlo salutare con dolcezza nella sua lingua madre. Le prime parole della giornata possono trasformare un semplice &quot;buongiorno&quot; in un momento di connessione profonda. Imparare i saluti e i congedi tedeschi insieme non è solo utile per la comunicazione quotidiana, ma crea momenti intimi che rafforzano il vostro legame. Queste 30 espressioni vi accompagneranno dalle prime ore del mattino fino all&#39;ultimo &quot;buonanotte&quot; condiviso.</p>\n<div class=\"speakable-phrase my-8 relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-rose-100 to-pink-100 rounded-2xl p-8\">\n  <div class=\"absolute top-4 right-4 text-6xl opacity-20\">💕</div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm uppercase tracking-wide text-accent font-bold mb-2\">\n    Frase da Imparare\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 font-header mb-2\">Ich liebe dich</p>\n  <p class=\"text-lg text-gray-600 mb-1\">Ti amo</p>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-accent\">[ ikh LEE-beh dikh ]</p>\n  <p class=\"mt-4 text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-4\">\n    La frase più importante da dire al tuo partner, ogni giorno.\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>I Saluti del Mattino: Iniziare la Giornata Insieme</h2>\n<p>I saluti mattutini in tedesco hanno un&#39;atmosfera speciale. Che tu voglia svegliare dolcemente il tuo partner o prepararti per una giornata lontano, queste espressioni creano momenti magici.</p>\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Guten Morgen, mein Schatz</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Buongiorno, mio tesoro</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">GOO-ten MOR-gen main shahts</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Guten Morgen, mein Schatz! Hast du gut geschlafen?\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Tedesco</th>\n<th>Italiano</th>\n<th>Pronuncia</th>\n<th>Quando Usare</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>Guten Morgen</strong></td>\n<td>Buongiorno</td>\n<td>GOO-ten MOR-gen</td>\n<td>Fino a mezzogiorno</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Morgen</strong></td>\n<td>Mattina</td>\n<td>MOR-gen</td>\n<td>Forma abbreviata informale</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Guten Tag</strong></td>\n<td>Buongiorno/Buonasera</td>\n<td>GOO-ten tahk</td>\n<td>Dalle 12 alle 18</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Hallo</strong></td>\n<td>Ciao</td>\n<td>HAH-loh</td>\n<td>Informale, sempre valido</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Grüß dich</strong></td>\n<td>Ti saluto</td>\n<td>gruess dikh</td>\n<td>Informale, regionale (sud)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Moin</strong></td>\n<td>Ciao/Buongiorno</td>\n<td>moin</td>\n<td>Nord della Germania</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Guten Abend</strong></td>\n<td>Buonasera</td>\n<td>GOO-ten AH-bent</td>\n<td>Dopo le 18</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<div class=\"my-8 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-2xl p-6\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl\">🇩🇪</span>\n    <h4 class=\"font-bold text-amber-800 font-header\">Northern Charm</h4>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"text-amber-900\">\n    <p>In nord Germania usano spesso &quot;Moin&quot; a tutte le ore! Non è solo mattutino - puoi dirlo anche la sera con il tuo partner per un tocco nordico.</p>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Saluti Romantici: Esclusivi per le Coppie</h2>\n<p>Quando siete soli, i saluti diventano più intimi. Queste espressioni creano momenti speciali tra voi due.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Mein Liebling</strong> (mio caro/mia cara) - &quot;main LEE-bling&quot;</li>\n<li><strong>Hallo, Süße</strong> (ciao, dolcezza) - &quot;HAH-loh, ZUE-seh&quot;</li>\n<li><strong>Tag, mein Herz</strong> (ciao, mio cuore) - &quot;tahk, main herts&quot;</li>\n<li><strong>Guten Morgen, Sonnenschein</strong> (buongiorno, raggio di sole) - &quot;GOO-ten MOR-gen, ZON-nen-shine&quot;</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>I Congedi: Dire Arrivederci con Amore</h2>\n<p>Il momento di separarsi può essere difficile, ma le giuste parole lo rendono più dolce. Impara a dire addio in modo affettuoso.</p>\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Auf Wiedersehen, mein Schatz</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Arrivederci, mio tesoro</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">owf VEE-der-zay-en main shahts</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Auf Wiedersehen, mein Schatz! Denk an mich!\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Tedesco</th>\n<th>Italiano</th>\n<th>Pronuncia</th>\n<th>Contesto</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>Auf Wiedersehen</strong></td>\n<td>Arrivederci</td>\n<td>owf VEE-der-zay-en</td>\n<td>Formale standard</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Tschüss</strong></td>\n<td>Ciao (congedo)</td>\n<td>chuess</td>\n<td>Informale quotidiano</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Bis später</strong></td>\n<td>A più tardi</td>\n<td>bis SHPAY-ter</td>\n<td>Nello stesso giorno</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Bis morgen</strong></td>\n<td>A domani</td>\n<td>bis MOR-gen</td>\n<td>Il giorno dopo</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Mach&#39;s gut</strong></td>\n<td>Stammi bene</td>\n<td>mahkhss goot</td>\n<td>Affettuoso informale</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Gute Nacht</strong></td>\n<td>Buonanotte</td>\n<td>GOO-teh nakht</td>\n<td>Prima di dormire</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Träum süß</strong></td>\n<td>Sogni d&#39;oro</td>\n<td>troyem zuess</td>\n<td>Romantico notturno</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<div class=\"my-8 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-2xl p-6\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl\">🇩🇪</span>\n    <h4 class=\"font-bold text-amber-800 font-header\">Regional <a href=\"/learn/it/de/german-greetings-and-goodbyes/\">Goodbye</a>s</h4>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"text-amber-900\">\n    <p>In Baviera e Austria usano &quot;Servus&quot; sia per salutare che per congedarsi - molto versatile con il tuo partner tedesco!</p>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Espressioni per Telefono e Messaggi</h2>\n<p>Quando non siete insieme fisicamente, queste frasi mantengono viva la connessione:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Hallo, hier bin ich</strong> (pronto, sono io) - &quot;HAH-loh, heer bin ikh&quot;</li>\n<li><strong>Ich rufe dich an</strong> (ti chiamo) - &quot;ikh ROO-feh dikh ahn&quot;</li>\n<li><strong>Wir hören uns</strong> (ci sentiamo) - &quot;veer HER-en uns&quot;</li>\n<li><strong>Bis gleich</strong> (a fra poco) - &quot;bis glykh&quot;</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Per scoprire come usare queste espressioni nei messaggi quotidiani, dai un&#39;occhiata alla nostra guida <a href=\"/learn/it/de/german-date-night-vocabulary/\">vocabolario per appuntamenti in tedesco</a>.</p>\n<h2>Saluti Speciali: Feste e Occasioni</h2>\n<p>Durante le festività, i saluti diventano ancora più significativi:</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Occasione</th>\n<th>Tedesco</th>\n<th>Italiano</th>\n<th>Pronuncia</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>Compleanno</td>\n<td><strong>Alles Gute zum Geburtstag!</strong></td>\n<td>Buon compleanno!</td>\n<td>AH-less GOO-teh tsoom geh-BOORTS-tahk</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Anniversario</td>\n<td><strong>Alles Liebe zum Jubiläum!</strong></td>\n<td>Tanti auguri per l&#39;anniversario!</td>\n<td>AH-less LEE-beh tsoom yoo-bee-LEH-om</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Anno Nuovo</td>\n<td><strong>Frohes neues Jahr!</strong></td>\n<td>Felice anno nuovo!</td>\n<td>FROH-es NOY-es yahr</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Natale</td>\n<td><strong>Frohe Weihnachten!</strong></td>\n<td>Buon Natale!</td>\n<td>FROH-eh VY-nakh-ten</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Pasqua</td>\n<td><strong>Frohe Ostern!</strong></td>\n<td>Buona Pasqua!</td>\n<td>FROH-eh OSS-tern</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2>Come Praticare Insieme</h2>\n<p>Per rendere questi saluti parte del vostro quotidiano, create piccoli rituali:</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Mattino</strong>: Stabilite un saluto mattutino preferito e usatelo sempre</li>\n<li><strong>Separazione</strong>: Scegliete un congedo speciale solo vostro</li>\n<li><strong>Serata</strong>: Create una formula &quot;buonanotte&quot; personale</li>\n<li><strong>Messaggi</strong>: Usate abbreviazioni come &quot;mS&quot; per &quot;mein Schatz&quot;</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Per evitare errori comuni quando usate queste espressioni, leggete la nostra guida sugli <a href=\"/learn/it/de/common-german-mistakes-italian-speakers-make/\">errori tedeschi più frequenti per italofoni</a>.</p>\n<h2>La Magia dei Piccoli Momenti</h2>\n<p>Imparare i saluti e i congedi tedeschi insieme non è solo questione di vocabolario - è un modo per creare momenti di connessione quotidiana. Quando il tuo partner ti dice &quot;Guten Morgen, mein Schatz&quot; o ti augura &quot;Träum süß&quot; prima di dormire, queste parole diventano parte intima del vostro rapporto.</p>\n<p>Le espressioni che abbiamo esplorato oggi sono solo l&#39;inizio del vostro viaggio linguistico. Ogni coppia ha il proprio modo speciale di salutarsi e congedarsi, e trovare le vostre frasi preferite renderà l&#39;apprendimento ancora più significativo.</p>"
  },
  {
    "id": "8e91da16-1a38-458f-82c4-3718c45e948d",
    "slug": "german-small-talk-conversation-starters",
    "title": "Conversazione in Tedesco: Frasi per Rompere il Ghiaccio",
    "links_added": 1,
    "content_html": "<p>Le grandi conversazioni spesso iniziano con piccole chiacchiere. Padroneggiare l&#39;arte dello small talk in tedesco ti permetterà di connetterti naturalmente con il tuo partner e la sua cerchia sociale.</p>\n<div class=\"speakable-phrase my-8 relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-rose-100 to-pink-100 rounded-2xl p-8\">\n  <div class=\"absolute top-4 right-4 text-6xl opacity-20\">💕</div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm uppercase tracking-wide text-accent font-bold mb-2\">\n    Frase da Imparare\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 font-header mb-2\">Wie war dein Tag?</p>\n  <p class=\"text-lg text-gray-600 mb-1\">Com'è andata la giornata?</p>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-accent\">[ vi var dain tag ]</p>\n  <p class=\"mt-4 text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-4\">\n    Una domanda perfetta per iniziare qualsiasi conversazione\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Iniziare una Conversazione</h2>\n<p>Frasi per rompere il ghiaccio.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>German</th>\n<th>Italiano</th>\n<th>Pronuncia</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>How are you?</td>\n<td>Come stai?</td>\n<td>hau ar yu</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>How was your day?</td>\n<td>Com&#39;è andata la giornata?</td>\n<td>hau woz yor dei</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>What&#39;s new?</td>\n<td>Che c&#39;è di nuovo?</td>\n<td>wots niu</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>What are you up to?</td>\n<td>Cosa stai facendo?</td>\n<td>wot ar yu ap tu</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Wie geht es dir?</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Come stai?</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">vi get es dir</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Wie geht es dir heute?\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"my-8 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-2xl p-6\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl\">🇩🇪</span>\n    <h4 class=\"font-bold text-amber-800 font-header\">Small Talk nella Cultura Tedesco</h4>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"text-amber-900\">\n    <p>Lo small talk varia tra culture ma è un modo universale per connettersi.</p>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Domande sulla Giornata</h2>\n<p>Come chiedere e raccontare della propria giornata.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>German</th>\n<th>Italiano</th>\n<th>Pronuncia</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>How was work?</td>\n<td>Com&#39;è andato il lavoro?</td>\n<td>hau woz werk</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Tell me about your day</td>\n<td>Raccontami della tua giornata</td>\n<td>tel mi a-baut</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Anything interesting happen?</td>\n<td>È successo qualcosa?</td>\n<td>E-ni-thing IN-te-res-ting</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2>Weekend e Tempo Libero</h2>\n<p>Argomenti leggeri e piacevoli.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>German</th>\n<th>Italiano</th>\n<th>Pronuncia</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>Any plans for the weekend?</td>\n<td>Programmi per il weekend?</td>\n<td>E-ni plans</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>What do you want to do?</td>\n<td>Cosa vuoi fare?</td>\n<td>wot du yu wont</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Let&#39;s do something fun</td>\n<td>Facciamo qualcosa di divertente</td>\n<td>lets du SAM-thing</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2>Reazioni e Risposte</h2>\n<p>Come reagire durante la conversazione.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>German</th>\n<th>Italiano</th>\n<th>Pronuncia</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>That&#39;s interesting!</td>\n<td>Che interessante!</td>\n<td>dats IN-te-res-ting</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Really?</td>\n<td>Davvero?</td>\n<td>RI-li</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>That <a href=\"/learn/it/de/german-pronunciation-guide-for-italian-speakers/\">sounds</a> great</td>\n<td>Sembra fantastico</td>\n<td>dat saunds greit</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Das ist interessant!</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Che interessante!</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">das ist IN-te-res-sant</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Das ist wirklich interessant!\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Consigli per lo Small Talk</h2>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Fai domande aperte</strong>: Evita risposte sì/no</li>\n<li><strong>Ascolta attivamente</strong>: Mostra interesse genuino</li>\n<li><strong>Condividi anche tu</strong>: È bidirezionale</li>\n<li><strong>Mantieni leggerezza</strong>: Evita argomenti pesanti</li>\n<li><strong>Pratica ogni giorno</strong>: Anche pochi minuti aiutano</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Per conversazioni più profonde, esplora le <a href=\"/german-expressing-emotions\">frasi per emozioni</a> e i <a href=\"/german-pet-names-terms-of-endearment\">vezzegiativi</a>.</p>"
  },
  {
    "id": "333af291-87c9-4825-a770-7890374b54e5",
    "slug": "german-texting-slang-for-couples",
    "title": "Slang Tedesco per Messaggi tra Innamorati",
    "links_added": 1,
    "content_html": "<h1>Slang Tedesco per Messaggi tra Innamorati</h1>\n<p>Quando il tuo partner tedesco ti scrive &quot;Hdl&quot; o &quot;Gn8&quot;, potresti rimanere confuso! Ecco la guida completa allo slang da messaggi in tedesco.</p>\n<h2>L&#39;Abbreviazione del Giorno</h2>\n<div class=\"speakable-phrase my-8 relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-rose-100 to-pink-100 rounded-2xl p-8\">\n  <div class=\"absolute top-4 right-4 text-6xl opacity-20\">💕</div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm uppercase tracking-wide text-accent font-bold mb-2\">\n    Frase da Imparare\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 font-header mb-2\">ILD</p>\n  <p class=\"text-lg text-gray-600 mb-1\">Ich liebe dich (Ti amo)</p>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-accent\">[ ish LI-be dish ]</p>\n  <p class=\"mt-4 text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-4\">\n    La dichiarazione d'amore più comune nei messaggi tedeschi\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Abbreviazioni d&#39;Amore</h2>\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">ILD</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Ich liebe dich (Ti amo)</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">ish LI-be dish</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Gute Nacht, ILD!\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Hdl</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Hab dich lieb (Ti voglio bene)</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">hab dish lip</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Bis später, hdl!\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Hdgdl</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Hab dich ganz doll lieb (Ti voglio tanto tanto bene)</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">hab dish gants dol lip</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Vermisse dich, hdgdl!\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Kuss / Bussi</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Bacio / Bacino</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">kus / BU-si</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Ciao Schatz, Bussi!\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"my-8 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-2xl p-6\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl\">🇩🇪</span>\n    <h4 class=\"font-bold text-amber-800 font-header\">ILD vs Hdl</h4>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"text-amber-900\">\n    <p>&quot;ILD&quot; (Ich liebe dich) è romantico e forte - riservato al partner. &quot;Hdl&quot; (Hab dich lieb) è più leggero, simile a &quot;ti voglio bene&quot;, usato anche con amici e famiglia. Con il partner puoi usare entrambi!</p>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Saluti nei Messaggi</h2>\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Hi / Hey</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Ciao</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">hai / hey</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Hi Schatz, wie geht's?\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Moin</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Ciao (Nord Germania)</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">mòin</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Moin! Alles klar?\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Servus</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Ciao (Baviera/Austria)</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">SER-vus</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Servus Schatzi!\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Domande Comuni</h2>\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Wg?</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Wie geht's? (Come stai?)</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">vi gets</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Hi, wg?\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Wo bist du?</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Dove sei?</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">vo bist du</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Hey, wo bist du?\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Was machst du?</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Cosa fai?</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">vas mahst du</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Was machst du gerade?\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Wann?</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Quando?</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">van</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Treffen wir uns? Wann?\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Risposte Rapide</h2>\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Ok / K</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Ok</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">o-KAY / KAH</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"K, bis später!\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Ja / Jo</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Sì</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">ya / yo</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Jo, machen wir!\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Ne / Nö</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">No (informale)</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">ne / neu</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Nö, heute nicht\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Lol / haha</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Risata</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">lol</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Lol das ist lustig!\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"my-8 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-2xl p-6\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl\">🇩🇪</span>\n    <h4 class=\"font-bold text-amber-800 font-header\">Emoji Tedeschi</h4>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"text-amber-900\">\n    <p>I tedeschi usano meno emoji rispetto ad altri paesi, ma i cuori e le faccine sono comuni nei messaggi romantici. Il cuore rosso significa &quot;ti amo&quot;. Un semplice &quot;:)&quot; è ancora molto usato!</p>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Abbreviazioni Utili</h2>\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Gn8</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Gute Nacht (Buonanotte)</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">GU-te naht</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Gn8 Schatz, träum süß!\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Gm</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Guten Morgen (Buongiorno)</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">GU-ten MOR-gen</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Gm! Kaffee?\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Bd</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Bis dann (A dopo)</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">bis dan</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Bd, hdl!\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Vllt</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Vielleicht (Forse)</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">fi-LAISHT</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Vllt morgen?\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Espressioni Affettuose</h2>\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Vermisse dich</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Mi manchi</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">fer-MI-se dish</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Vermisse dich so sehr!\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Freu mich auf dich</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Non vedo l'ora di vederti</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">froi mish auf dish</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Freu mich auf heute Abend!\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Kp</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Kein Problem (Nessun problema)</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">kain pro-BLEM</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Kp, machen wir morgen!\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Np</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Nessun problema</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">kain pro-BLEM</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Np, ich warte!\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Pro<a href=\"/learn/it/de/german-grammar-basics-for-beginners/\">grammar</a>e Incontri</h2>\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Treffen?</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Ci vediamo?</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">TRE-fen</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Treffen wir uns heute?\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Wann + Wo?</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Quando e dove?</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">van + vo</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Ok, wann + wo?\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Bis gleich</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">A fra poco</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">bis glaish</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Bin unterwegs, bis gleich!\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Komme</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Sto arrivando</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">KO-me</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Komme in 10 min!\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Espressioni Moderne</h2>\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Mega</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Super, fantastico</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">ME-ga</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Das war mega!\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Krass</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Incredibile, forte</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">kras</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Krass, echt jetzt?\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Digga</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Amico (slang giovane)</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">DI-ga</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Digga, das ist verrückt!\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"my-8 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-2xl p-6\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl\">🇩🇪</span>\n    <h4 class=\"font-bold text-amber-800 font-header\">Formalità nei Messaggi</h4>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"text-amber-900\">\n    <p>I tedeschi tendono ad essere più formali anche nei messaggi rispetto ad altri paesi. Con il partner puoi essere informale, ma non usare slang troppo giovane se il tuo partner è più adulto - potrebbe sembrare strano!</p>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Tabella Riassuntiva</h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Abbreviazione</th>\n<th>Significato</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>ILD</td>\n<td>Ti amo</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Hdl</td>\n<td>Ti voglio bene</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Gn8</td>\n<td>Buonanotte</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Gm</td>\n<td>Buongiorno</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Wg</td>\n<td>Come stai?</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Bd</td>\n<td>A dopo</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Vllt</td>\n<td>Forse</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Kp</td>\n<td>Nessun problema</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>"
  }
]
